snippet.title: Pressure Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy Pressure on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/224220/

Race, ram & blast!

Pressure is a unique combination of breakneck racing-action and arcade styled shoot'em up in a steampunk world filled with crazy characters and funky humor.

Pressure is our first game to be published. We hope you like it!

Coming: March 26th, available as digital download (eg. via Steam).

More Infos:
http://chasing-carrots.com/games.php
http://www.facebook.com/ChasingCarrotsGames
https://twitter.com/chasing_carrots
